snippet.title: SuperOffice Trailer #1
snippet.description:
SuperOffice is a top-down action-roguelike game where time moves only when you move. One day you discovered all your work colleagues were kidnapped by aliens and a jewel you found on your desk drawer allows you to manipulate time. Either this is a very crazy day or your office will never be the same.

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1576080/SuperOffice
